---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="計畫說明 - WZULTC" description="台灣長照產業跨域整合與場域實踐之研究 - 以跨國移工文化適應與專業照護技能升級為例">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-5xl">
    <!-- Page Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">
        台灣長照產業跨域整合與場域實踐之研究
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
        以跨國移工文化適應與專業照護技能升級為例
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="space-y-8">
      <!-- Vision & Mission -->
      <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 via-cyan-500 to-teal-500 rounded-xl p-8 text-white text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">
          願景：共創長照無礙
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl opacity-90">
          核心使命：培育跨域人才、深耕實踐場域
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Introduction -->
      <section class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">
          計畫緣起
        </h2>
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
          <p>
            文藻跨語照護計畫（WZULTC）致力於提供越南移工優質的華語教學與文化適應支援，
            促進跨文化理解與社會共融。
          </p>
          <p>
            隨著台灣長照產業的發展，越來越多越南移工投入照護工作。然而，語言與文化差異
            往往成為他們融入台灣社會的最大挑戰。本計畫透過專業的華語教學、雙語學伴支援，
            以及創新的教學模式，協助越南移工克服語言障礙，提升照護專業能力。
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- 三大核心目標 -->
      <section class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 text-center">
          三大核心目標
        </h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-cyan-50 rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-cyan-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">就醫無障礙</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">高榮外籍人士就醫綠色通道，導入 AI 雙向翻譯系統</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-50 to-teal-50 rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500 to-teal-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">CareConnect</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">多國語智慧學習與 AI 互動平台</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-50 to-green-50 rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500 to-green-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">專技護升級</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">華語/文化與多國語照護培訓</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- 計畫成果 -->
      <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-cyan-50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8 text-center">
          計畫成果
        </h2>
        <!-- 數據統計 -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-teal-600 mb-1">11+</div>
            <div class="text-gray-700">場活動</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-1">290+</div>
            <div class="text-gray-700">人次參與</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-cyan-600 mb-1">31</div>
            <div class="text-gray-700">堂線上課程</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 精選活動 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">精選活動</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>SNQ 國家品質標章委員實地訪查</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>多元文化交織的照護現場講座</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>旗津日照中心參訪 + 音樂療法體驗</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>華語教學實體課程</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- 教學創新 -->
      <section class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 text-center">
          教學創新
        </h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="border-l-4 border-teal-500 pl-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">跨語言化</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">越南籍小老師中越雙語教學，降低學習門檻</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">微課設計</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">50 分鐘內完成有效學習，符合工作節奏</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-l-4 border-cyan-500 pl-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">多模態</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">視覺化教材 + 手機友善 + 音檔輔助</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- 技術亮點：AI AMAZE -->
      <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-indigo-50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <div class="md:flex items-center gap-8">
          <div class="md:w-1/3 text-center mb-6 md:mb-0">
            <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-indigo-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">AI AMAZE</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600">愛吠的狗團隊開發</p>
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-2/3">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">專業醫療翻譯系統</h3>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-purple-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                  <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">1</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800">技術架構</p>
                  <p class="text-gray-600">LLM + RAG（大型語言模型 + 檢索增強生成）</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-indigo-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                  <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">2</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800">核心優勢</p>
                  <p class="text-gray-600">醫療術語 100% 精準翻譯</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-violet-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                  <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">3</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800">應用情境</p>
                  <p class="text-gray-600">就醫即時翻譯 / 自助學習模式</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- 四大亮點 -->
      <section class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 text-center">
          四大亮點
        </h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-cyan-50 rounded-lg">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-blue-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-white font-bold">1</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800">首創「跨語言化」照護華語教學模式</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-1">突破傳統單語教學限制</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-50 to-teal-50 rounded-lg">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-cyan-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-white font-bold">2</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800">導入 AI 專業醫療翻譯技術</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-1">科技賦能語言學習</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-50 to-green-50 rounded-lg">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-teal-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-white font-bold">3</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800">產學醫三方合作創新典範</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-1">跨領域資源整合</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-50 to-emerald-50 rounded-lg">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-white font-bold">4</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800">回應長照 3.0 與超高齡社會需求</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-1">前瞻政策對接</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- 執行資訊 -->
      <section class="bg-gray-100 rounded-xl p-8">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-center">
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-1">執行單位</p>
            <p class="font-bold text-gray-800">文藻外語大學 x 高雄榮民總醫院</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-1">執行期程</p>
            <p class="font-bold text-gray-800">2024 - 2025</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-1">補助單位</p>
            <p class="font-bold text-gray-800">國家科學及技術委員會（NSTC）</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Contact CTA -->
      <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 via-cyan-500 to-teal-500 rounded-xl p-8 text-center text-white">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">
          想了解更多？
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6 opacity-90">
          歡迎與我們聯繫，了解更多計畫詳情
        </p>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-block bg-white text-teal-600 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors"
        >
          聯絡我們
        </a>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
